- Land Use Urban: 8 ft sidewalk + 2 ft buffer + parking OR 8 ft sidewalk + 4 ft buffer OR 8 ft sidewalk + 6 ft buffer
- Land Use Suburban: 6 ft sidewalk + 2 ft buffer + parking OR 6 ft sidewalk + 4 ft buffer OR 6 ft sidewalk + 6 ft buffer
- If the dimensions shown exceed the dimensions given by the PLTS tables, then use the values in the PLTS table as the minimum allowable dimensions.
- Vehicle posted speed (mph) ≤15 20 25 30 35 ≥40[[SRC_1]]

